text: Agent Events An agent event is an information message from the agent that can be used when configuring an event notification in an Event Notifications configuration, see Agent Event for more information about this event type. There are no agent events for this agent. Debug Events A debug event is an event that is dispatched when debug is used, and can be used when configuring an event notification in an Event Notifications configuration, see Debug Event for more information about this event type. There are no debug events for this agent.
